# Among-Check Core

**Tagline:** Find imposters among codebase.

## Before coding

Read `docs/architecture.md`, `AGENTS.md`, `docs/scanner-catalog.md`, and `audits/latest.toon` (security context).

## Structure

- pnpm monorepo: `packages/core`, `packages/cli`, `packages/mcp`, `packages/agents`, `packages/shared`
- Scanners implement `Scanner` from `core`; register in `packages/agents/src/index.ts`

## Requirements

- Every `Finding` includes `aiFixPrompt` via `buildAiFixPrompt()`
- Scanner IDs match `docs/scanner-catalog.md` (`{category}.{kebab-name}`)
- Non-destructive probes; redact secrets in evidence
- Minimal diffs; no unrelated refactors

## Audit archive

- Every scan writes `audits/` in TOON and git-commits by default (`archiveScanReport()`)
- See `docs/audit-archive.md` and `docs/architecture.md` §14
- Check `delta.toon` for new/resolved findings after fixes

## Phases

Follow implementation phases in `docs/architecture.md` §10 (Phase 0 scaffold first).
